Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.21,0:00:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If this continues,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.36,0:00:04.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)このままでは\N必ず 第２第３の包帯悪魔が現れ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there will be more rag demons in our future\Nrising up to oppose mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:06.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,人間に牙をむくでしょう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You're so cute, Mugaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.98,0:00:09.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅ･ﾄﾞﾗﾝｺﾞ)\Nムガロちゃん かわいいです～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.62,0:00:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あいつ 早く戻ってくるといいね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he comes back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:15.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｿﾌｨｴﾙ)\N昼に 例の子供の力が発動された｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.89,0:00:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The child unleashed his power\Nthis afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.65,0:00:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you have been this much of\Na pathetic crybaby ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.79,0:00:18.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)１０年前のあんたは\Nそんなに ウジウジ ウジウジ➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウダウダしてたかしらね｡\N(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)必ず➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a path where\Nall three races can live in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.61,0:00:22.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,三種族が共に生きる道が\Nあるはずです｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:24.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は それを諦めない！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will never give up on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:27.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽ17世)お前は\Nお前の思うように生きてみよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.86,0:00:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You live your life your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be doing what I feel is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.70,0:00:30.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は 私の正義を貫くだけだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:33.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,変態！\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)うわぁ～～！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)はい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.39,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.85,0:00:59.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ニ… ニーナちゃん\Nこれでいいかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.98,0:01:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:04.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ？\Nニーナちゃ～ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.82,0:01:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:08.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しつこい 変態｡\Nえっ あぁ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.03,0:01:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop bothering me, pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ…｡\Nお嬢さん 思い出してください➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.08,0:01:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Young lady...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please remember how Bacchus\Nkindly opened up his home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.68,0:01:17.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行き場のなクワァったあなたに\N住居を提供してくれた➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.87,0:01:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,to provide you a place to stay\Nwhen you had nowhere else to turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あのバッカスの優しさを｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.69,0:01:21.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知らない｡\Nクワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.54,0:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's a bit cruel to dismiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.71,0:01:24.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢知らない｣は\Nクワァわいそうでしょう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.63,0:01:27.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)ニーナ\N唐辛子と手羽先が足らないの｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.67,0:01:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, we don't have enough chili peppers\Nand chicken wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:30.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,買ってきてくれない？\Nは～い｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.93,0:01:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you go buy some?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.18,0:01:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.09,0:01:35.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)今年も\Nこの手羽先料理ですクワァ？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.18,0:01:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making chicken wings again\Nthis year? They were a big hit last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,去年は 大繁盛でしたねぇ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:40.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)\Nもっと買っておけばよかったわ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've bought more.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.19,0:01:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina will be in quite the predicament\Nif that handsome man
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.61,0:01:43.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うわさのイケメンが食べに来て\N売り切れだったら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.02,0:01:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,shows up and we're out of wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.18,0:01:45.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナが困るしね｡\Nえっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.52,0:01:49.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)そうですねぇ｡ あの\N腕相撲をしたイケメンが来たら➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.69,0:01:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right. If that handsome man\Nyou arm wrestled shows up,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.87,0:01:53.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぜひ 食べさせたいですね｡\Nちょっと やめてよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.16,0:01:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we've got to let him try some.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, cut that out!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.54,0:01:56.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰だ その男！ 俺は知らねぇぞ！\Nんんっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.62,0:01:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this man you're talking about?\NNobody told me about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:59.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)あっ あっ…｡\N(ﾊﾝｻ)あれは いい男でしたねぇ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:01:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He sure was a handsome man.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:02.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ノーブルで 威厳がありましたよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He had a noble dignity about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.63,0:02:06.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)来てくれるといいわねぇ｡\Nいってきま～す｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-I hope he comes.\N-I'm off, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.02,0:02:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ～あ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know, Rita?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:14.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)知ってます？ リタさん｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina still keeps the ring that the man\Nleft behind that day in her pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.81,0:02:18.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お嬢さんは あの日\N例の男が置いていった指輪を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:21.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いつまでも大事に\Nポケットに入れてるんですよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.72,0:02:24.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)あらあら 随分 乙女チックね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My, how girly of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この前までは アザゼルに\Nさんざん 顔を赤らめてたのに｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.90,0:02:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't that long ago that she was\Nblushing from Azazel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.90,0:02:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The heart is a fickle thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.96,0:02:31.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,心は移ろうものですクワァら｡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.88,0:02:34.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クワッ クワッ クワッ\Nクワッ クワッ クワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.26,0:02:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.19,0:04:16.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ･回想)((必ず 三種族が\N共に生きる道があるはずです｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.34,0:04:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be a path where\Nall three races can live in peace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.26,0:04:18.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私は それを諦めない！))
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.59,0:04:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And I will never give up on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとう！\N(ﾊﾟﾝ屋)おっ ニーナ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-Thanks!\N-Oh, Nina!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.30,0:04:36.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ｡\N戦勝記念のパンを焼いたから➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.20,0:04:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I baked some bread for the celebration!\NWhy don't you take a loaf?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.35,0:04:38.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,持っていきな｡\Nいいの？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.87,0:04:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.20,0:04:43.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今日のは\N切れっ端じゃないぞ～｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And these aren't your usual leftovers.\NThis is hot and fresh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:46.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,焼きたてだ｡\Nやった～！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.96,0:04:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:48.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ありがとうです～｡\N(ﾊﾟﾝ屋)にひっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.20,0:04:51.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふふっ｡ あっ あら？ あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:57.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(奴隷使いﾎﾞｽ)待ちな！\Nあっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:03.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,はぁ～ また あんたなの？ 何よ？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You again? What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I promised didn't I?\NI'm here to make you my slave.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.98,0:05:08.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,約束どおり お嬢ちゃんを\N俺の奴隷にしてやろうと思ってな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:22.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドクン ドクン ドクン…(鼓動)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(手下)この… おらっ！\Nうわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.50,0:05:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ 私のお肉！\Nあっ ちょっ… ああっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No! My meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.01,0:05:37.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドカッ！\Nうっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.85,0:05:44.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ぐっ！\Nどうした？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Can't do anything\Nwhen you're on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.62,0:05:46.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１人じゃ何もできねぇか？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.23,0:05:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:53.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫(市民)やめてやれよ！\N≫(市民)まだ子供だろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.44,0:05:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,She's still just a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:04.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(心の声)≪もう嫌 この体！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.45,0:06:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate my body so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:06.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(手下)なんだ？ 貴様｡\Nあっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell do you think you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.64,0:06:08.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ痛たたたっ！ うわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.75,0:06:23.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(手下)てめぇ… うわっ！\N(奴隷使いﾎﾞｽ)ぐっ！ おととっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-Damn you!\N-Whoa, whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.91,0:06:26.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そりゃ！ うわっ ぐわっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.22,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.21,0:06:31.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あれは…｡\N(手下)うっ ぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.11,0:06:41.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おい 行くぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.65,0:06:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:57.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≫コツ コツ(足音)\N≪やばい…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.84,0:06:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God. This is bad.\NThis is bad. This is so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.34,0:06:59.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪やばい やばい やばい やばい≫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:24.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腕力だけでなく 足も速いのだな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only are you strong,\Nbut you're fast as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.08,0:07:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you not fight back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:30.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ 彼らに抵抗しなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.12,0:07:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.22,0:07:34.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは\N私 女の子だから…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm a girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.88,0:07:36.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なぜ 顔を上げない？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.04,0:07:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:41.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナだったな｡\Nえっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.22,0:07:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.27,0:07:46.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,覚えていてくれたんですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.07,0:07:48.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私に何か用か？\Nはっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.10,0:07:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you need something from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.21,0:07:53.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あ… あの… 今夜➡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight is the night before Anatae's\Nbig festival, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.31,0:07:57.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アナティのお祭りの前夜祭でしょ｡\Nああ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be running a food stand with a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:08:00.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間と屋台を出すんです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,助けてもらったお礼がしたいので\N来てくれませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.03,0:08:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for helping me,\Nso would you come by?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.44,0:08:08.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この前 腕相撲した馬車が\N目印です｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.62,0:08:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll know it from the carriage\Nwhen we arm wrestled.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.85,0:08:11.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか 分かった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.87,0:08:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"I see. Very well," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:17.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢そうか 分かった｣… か｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.76,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,"I see. Very well."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,｢そうか 分かった｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:33.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか 分かった｣｡ へへへっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"I see. Very well."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:37.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ？\N(ﾘﾀ)ん？ 遅かったじゃない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you so long?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.94,0:08:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to these peppers?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:46.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)何よ このへたれた唐辛子！\N(ﾊﾝｻ)お肉は？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,落としちゃった｡\N(ﾊﾝｻ)落とした!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I dropped it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You dropped it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.69,0:08:50.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)\N落としたら拾えばいいじゃない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.91,0:08:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why didn't you just pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうか…｡\N(ﾘﾀ)ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:56.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いや 踏んづけられちゃったの｡\N(ﾊﾝｻ)誰に？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.96,0:08:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,-It got stepped on!\N-By who?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:09:00.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,悪い人たち｡\Nえっ… 何よ それ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.75,0:08:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,By bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ごめんなさい｡\Nまあいいわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.04,0:09:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.17,0:09:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.45,0:09:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,このへたれた唐辛子で\N料理しましょう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to make do\Nwith these sad peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.37,0:09:09.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手羽先は ある分だけで…｡ ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.47,0:09:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess these\Nare all the wings we'll have.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.93,0:09:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she's shocked\Nfrom dropping the chicken wings.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)手羽先を落としちゃったのが\Nショックなのでしょうクワァ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what I told him,\Nbut what if he really shows up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:20.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あんなこと言っちゃったけど\Nほんとに来たら どうしよう…≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.98,0:09:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll turn into a dragon. I just know I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.03,0:09:24.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪私 竜になっちゃう｡\N絶対なっちゃう～！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:28.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来る｡ 来ない｡ 来る｡ 来ない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.74,0:09:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come. He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come. He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来る｡ 来ない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll come. He won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:34.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クワッ… 何してるんですクワァ！\Nやめてくださいよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Stop that please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:39.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何してんですかって…｡\Nあははっ ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.29,0:09:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドサッ！\N(ﾊﾝｻ)しどい…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.08,0:09:47.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(側近)陛下！\Nん？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Your Majesty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.11,0:09:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今まで どちらに お出ましに\Nなっておられたのですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.60,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You must tell one of us\Nwhen you decide to leave the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.72,0:09:55.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お出ましのときは 必ず\Nおっしゃっていただきませんと｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:57.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,黙れ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.02,0:09:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.24,0:10:08.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)明日の正午\N人間どものパレードが出発する｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Tomorrow afternoon, the humans\Nwill be putting on a parade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:10.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パレードは\N城の正門からスタートし➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,The parade will begin\Nfrom the castle gates,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:13.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,城下の中央通りを進み➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,proceed down the center of the city,\Nmake its way around the plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:16.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,広場で迂回して\N城へと戻るルートだ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and return to the castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ポイントとなるのは\Nこの場所だ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The crucial point will be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは パレードを\Nここで止める必要がある｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The parade will need to be\Nstopped here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.59,0:10:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use that as a signal to come down\Nfrom the north here with the red dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:26.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は それを合図に\Nここから 赤い竜と共に南下する｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.95,0:10:28.95,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾀﾞﾝﾃ)挟み撃ちか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A pincer attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.26,0:10:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The soldiers in black armor should prove\Nthe most troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:34.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)最も厄介なのは\Nあの黒い鎧の連中だ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.54,0:10:37.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が\Nヤツらを赤い竜に引き付ける｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I will draw them to the red dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,残った兵と人間の王を➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.02,0:10:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,While I do, you will split up into two groups
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.20,0:10:44.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふた手に分かれた貴様らで\N総攻撃を仕掛けるのだ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.31,0:10:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and attack the remaining troops\Nand their king.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第一部隊は\N高台からの遠距離攻撃｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The first squad will conduct a range attack\Nfrom high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.74,0:10:52.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,第二部隊は\N接近戦により 確実に王を殺せ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.86,0:10:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The second squad will engage in\Nclose combat and slay the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But this plan\Nrelies heavily on the red dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.04,0:10:58.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾀﾞﾝﾃ)しかし\N完全に 赤い竜頼みの作戦だな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do is trust you.\NThere's no room for failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.87,0:11:01.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは\Nお前を ただ信じるしかない｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.43,0:11:03.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,失敗は許されんぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think you're talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.71,0:11:07.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)誰に言っている｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage of Bahamut
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.85,0:11:21.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パン パン パン パン！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.98,0:11:35.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)\N街は こんなに浮かれてるのに➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.99,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The town's so festive...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.72,0:11:39.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なんか さえないっすね 俺たち｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:39.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Apart from us, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.72,0:11:42.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,団長は\N何も感じないんすかね この状況｡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.83,0:11:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that make you feel, Captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:49.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((お前は\Nお前の思うように生きてみよ))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.13,0:11:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You live your life your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:52.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,((私は 私の正義を貫くだけだ))
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.09,0:11:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be doing what I feel is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.77,0:12:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dias, I am leaving you in charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.82,0:12:12.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)ディアス ここは任せる！\N(ﾃﾞｨｱｽ)はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.35,0:12:15.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱﾚｻﾝﾄﾞ)ま～た単独行動かよ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.49,0:12:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes off on his own again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:32.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダダダダ… ダン！\Nあっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.05,0:12:46.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)いらっしゃい いらっしゃい｡\Nここの手羽先 おいしいよ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, welcome!\NWe have delicious wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.94,0:12:50.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 俺のが もっとうまいよ｡\N食べさせないけどね！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.06,0:12:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But mine taste even better,\Nnot that I'll let you eat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:53.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾘﾀ)そんなに呼び込んだら\N間に合わないわ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.52,0:12:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll run out if you draw that many in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.34,0:12:55.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)はい どうぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.36,0:12:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:58.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ニーナ ぼう～っとしないの｡\N危ないでしょ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, stop spacing out. It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.67,0:13:01.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,は～い｡ ふふっ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.45,0:13:05.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)いらっしゃい いらっしゃい｡\N唐辛子焼きは絶品だよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, welcome!\NOur spicy wings are to die for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.71,0:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:08.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)\Nニ… ニーナちゃん 大丈夫か？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you leave me alone please?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.54,0:13:11.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほっといていただけませんか？\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)あっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.38,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now! These wings are perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:15.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,さあさあ\N祭りの夜には ぴったりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,for a festive night like this!\NThey'll light a fire in your belly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.48,0:13:21.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,腹から燃えるよ｡ あっ\Nおにいさん お久しぶりですね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.22,0:13:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hey there, young man!\NGood to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)これが うわさの\N腕相撲のイケメンですよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.23,0:13:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the handsome guy\Nfrom the arm wrestling we mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.35,0:13:31.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふ～ん なかなかね｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.86,0:13:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:38.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,１つ 返し忘れた｡\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.20,0:13:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to return one to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:44.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ…｡\Nい… いらっしゃいませ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.36,0:13:47.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)おい 若ぇの｡\Nなんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there, youngblood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.58,0:13:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ちょ… ちょっと バッカス\N何してんのよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Bacchus?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.57,0:13:54.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)\Nうちの手羽先は うめぇんだが➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.80,0:13:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Our wings are great,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.84,0:13:58.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,スペシャルは これで終わりだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.05,0:13:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,but this is the last of our special.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.12,0:14:02.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいのか？ 私がもらっても｡\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ああ｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you want me to have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:04.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そのかわりと言っちゃなんだが\Nこの子と➡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.14,0:14:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But would you do me a favor
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,and take this girl\Naround to see the festival with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.85,0:14:07.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前夜祭を見て回ってくれねぇか？\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ガキのくせに\N意外と胸は でけぇ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's got a big chest for her age.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.97,0:14:13.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふんっ！\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)うぐっ！ どわ～っと！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.26,0:14:15.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バ～ッカじゃないの？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.65,0:14:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,-You're so stupid.\N-Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:17.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かった｡\Nえっ!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.19,0:14:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Say what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.33,0:14:19.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.35,0:14:21.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これを食べたら行こう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.45,0:14:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go after I finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:26.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ドクン ドクン ドクン…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:36.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パン パン パン パン！\N(一同)おお～！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like one?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:59.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,食べるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.38,0:15:07.64,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あぁ～…｡\Nそれは むいて食べるんだ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.91,0:15:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You are supposed to peel it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.64,0:15:11.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ｡ あっ… 知ってるわよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.96,0:15:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that! Of course I knew that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.25,0:15:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,知ってますとも｡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:17.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おいしい！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.09,0:15:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ほんとに大丈夫かしら？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.81,0:16:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter how great he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.14,0:16:14.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくら すてきっていったって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,This is her first time\Ngoing out alone with a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:16.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,男の人と\N二人っきりで出かけるなんて➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めてでしょ？\N(ﾊﾝｻ)大人になって➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.94,0:16:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She might come back all grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:21.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,帰って来るかもしれませんね｡\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)ぶぅ～～！➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:24.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おい！\N(ﾘﾀ)あんたが唆したんでしょ？➡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who put them up to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.22,0:16:29.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ったく…｡ 祭りの最中に\N竜にでもなったら大惨事よ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better hope she doesn't turn into\Na dragon in the middle of the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.04,0:16:31.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾊﾝｻ)クワッ…｡\N(ﾊﾞｯｶｽ)うぅ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:47.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やってみるか｡\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.88,0:16:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like to try?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:51.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,む… 無理だよ\N私 こんな踊り知らないし｡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.51,0:16:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I can't.\NI don't know this dance at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.64,0:18:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How was I able to dance like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪なんで\N私 踊れちゃったんだろう≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.92,0:18:20.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪あんな近くで顔を見て\Nしかも 手まで握っちゃって≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.02,0:18:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I got so close to him,\Nand we even held hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:23.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,≪ああ～ 無理 無理 無理！≫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.15,0:18:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't danced like that\Nsince I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:26.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,踊ったのは子供のとき以来だ｡\Nえっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You were quite good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.49,0:18:28.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,なかなか うまかったじゃないか｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:32.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うっ…｡\N初めてには感じなかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.36,0:18:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It did not feel like your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:35.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そ… そんな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.78,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.20,0:18:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the first time\NI've danced with a man,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.25,0:18:38.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私 男の人とダンスをしたのも➡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,街を二人っきりで歩いたのも\N初めてです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.71,0:18:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and the first time I've been out alone\Nin the city with one like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.86,0:18:43.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,私もだ｡\Nうそ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.21,0:18:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Me as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, right!\NYou were so good at dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.88,0:18:46.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ダンス\Nあんなに上手だったじゃない｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ｡\Nダンスはできる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.01,0:18:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how to dance, but I have never\Nwalked around the city with a lady before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.58,0:18:53.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし\N女性と街を歩いたことはなかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:58.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽しかった｡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:19:00.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うぐっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you tell me your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.85,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,教えて あなたの名前｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.74,0:19:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,My name? My name is
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.85,0:19:13.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,名前か…｡ 名前は➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:16.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クリス｡\Nクリス…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Chris.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.70,0:19:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I see you again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.78,0:19:22.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また会える？ また踊りたい｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.25,0:19:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to dance with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:27.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは分からない｡\Nどうして？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.74,0:19:31.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,また会えるといいな｡\Nえっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.43,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can see each other again.\NI hope we can see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.52,0:19:35.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｼｬﾘｵｽの声)会えるといいな｡\N会えるといいな｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.18,0:19:38.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,会えるといいな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.39,0:19:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope we can see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.55,0:19:43.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ワン ワン！\Nワン ワン！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.48,0:19:56.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)ぐわっ！ ううっ…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.75,0:20:02.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,痛ててっ…｡ あっ ごめんなさい！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.87,0:20:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.42,0:20:04.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)ちっ お前か｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.79,0:20:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.92,0:20:08.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,誰？\N(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)俺だ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:12.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,アザゼル！ どこ行ってたのよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Azazel! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:14.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ムガロちゃんのことを\N置いてきぼりにして｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.42,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you leave Mugaro like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:18.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)時が来た｡\Nえっ？ 何？ なんの時？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.97,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.14,0:20:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.81,0:20:24.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)明日 パレードが始まったら\Nあの塔の下に来い｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,When the parade begins tomorrow,\Ngo to that tower there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:26.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それじゃない｡ こっち｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that one, this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.61,0:20:29.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… ごめん｡\N(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)必ず来い｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.02,0:20:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me you'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.49,0:20:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What was with his attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:40.56,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何よ 威張っちゃって｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:53.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)ちっ｡ また お前か｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.12,0:20:55.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｶｲｻﾞﾙ)こんな所で何をしている？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.68,0:20:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparing for the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ｱｻﾞｾﾞﾙ)祭りの準備さ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:21:00.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何をするつもりだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.15,0:21:05.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ふふふっ｡ 楽しみにしてろ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.14,0:21:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.82,0:21:09.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貴様らの記念日を\N俺たちも盛大に祝ってやる｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We will be joining you\Nin your big day of celebration.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.02,0:21:28.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(ﾆｰﾅの声)｢お母さん 今日\N私の中で 何かが はじけました｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.12,0:21:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Dear Mom,\NSomething happened to me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:33.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな衝撃は\N生まれて初めてです｡➡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never felt this way before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.01,0:21:35.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もしかして｣…｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.09,0:21:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,パン パン パン パン！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.94,0:21:48.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これが 恋!?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.10,0:21:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this love?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.83,0:22:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, it's okay\NI cast the usual spell
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stagnation, stagnation\NMy words and heart are at odds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.04,0:22:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Default\NI've taken all the paint
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And mixed up all the colors\NUntil you're left with me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.72,0:22:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So fragile\NYet strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Close to overflowing\NBut not spilling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.97,0:22:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm incomplete\NI won't amount to much
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.98,0:22:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a good luck charm\NI'm not asking for your help
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just a good luck charm\NI was just clinging to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.57,0:22:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it all today\NI'm done living this pointless life
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.87,0:22:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's end it all today\NI've taken my last pointless breath
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:22:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom it may concern\NSee ya and goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.59,0:23:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I killed the person I was yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.64,0:23:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,To whom it may concern\NSee ya and goodbye
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A new morning is coming
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.16,0:23:45.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,行くぞ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.01,0:23:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.89,0:23:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Charioce!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.18,0:23:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,-Raggy!\N-Raggy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.93,0:23:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't it uncomfortable to be wrapped\Nup so tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.35,0:23:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,-The rags stretch!\N-Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.81,0:23:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Rage of Bahamut:\NVirgin Soul, "The Day of Victory."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.32,0:24:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Raggy! Oh, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.11,0:24:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Soul!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.99,0:24:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Baha Baha Baha Soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.24,0:24:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I demand you watch\Nthe next episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.24,0:24:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare disappoint me.
